{"id": "duc04-testb-2:6#18", "contents": "Swiss IOC executive board member Marc Hodler sparked controversy on Sunday by suggesting he might be expelled from the International Olympic Committee (IOC) due to his allegations of corruption within the Olympic movement. When questioned about the possibility of resignation, Hodler responded, \"No, I don't resign. But maybe I will be expelled. You never know.\" His comments came a day after he made the allegations, which have caused a stir within the IOC."}
